  <FCP_Quest_FeralGhoulInfestation.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription-&gt;[asker_nameFull] of [asker_faction_name] reports: &quot;We've got a serious problem - a pack of feral ghouls has taken over [location]. They've been attacking any scavengers who get too close. The place likely has valuable pre-war salvage, but nobody's getting in while those ferals are nesting there. Clear them out and you can keep whatever you find inside.&quot;</FCP_Quest_FeralGhoulInfestation.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
